About Escorts Finance

Escorts Finance is in the Finance - Leasing & Hire Purchase sector. The current market capitalisation stands at Rs 33.01 crore.The company management includes Pritam Narang - Whole Time Director, Rochak Puri - Director, Preeti Chauhan - Director, Rochak Puri - Director, Preeti Chauhan - Director. It is listed on the BSE with a BSE Code of 511716 and the NSE with an NSE Code of ESCORTSFIN.Its Registered office is at SCO - 198-200, Second Floor,,Sector - 34A, Chandigarh,Chandigarh - 160022.Their Registrars are Alankit Assignment Ltd.








