About Escorts

Escorts is in the Auto - Tractors sector. The current market capitalisation stands at Rs 8,308.26 crore.The company management includes Rajan Nanda - Chairman & Managing Director, Nikhil Nanda - Managing Director, Nitasha Nanda - Director, Hardeep Singh - Director, P H Ravikumar - Director, Vibha Paul Rishi - Director, Sutanu Behuria - Director, G B Mathur - Director, D J Kakalia - Additional Director, G B Mathur - Director, D J Kakalia - Additional Director. It is listed on the BSE with a BSE Code of 500495 and the NSE with an NSE Code of ESCORTS.Its Registered office is at 15/5,  Mathura Road, , Faridabad,Haryana - 121003.Their Registrars are Karvy Computershare Private Ltd.








